"},{"tags":["box-api"],"owner":{"reputation":334,"user_id":2918349,"user_type":"registered","accept_rate":72,"profile_image":"https://i.stack.imgur.com/eH0rA.png?s=128&g=1","display_name":"Aaron","link":"https://stackoverflow.com/users/2918349/aaron"},"is_answered":true,"view_count":514,"accepted_answer_id":34594711,"answer_count":1,"score":2,"last_activity_date":1480966298,"creation_date":1450046932,"question_id":34257330,"link":"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/34257330/what-is-the-intended-use-case-for-app-auth-and-app-users","title":"What is the intended use case for app auth and app users?","body":"<p>I am trying to understand what is the intended use case for app auth and app users. Im basically thinking about building an app that would use Box to store data of users that would subscribe to our service. Our service would allow each user to access and view their data.</p>

