"},{"tags":["file-upload","box-api","postman","box"],"owner":{"reputation":48,"user_id":5626619,"user_type":"registered","accept_rate":86,"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/92064937ab1c262d9bc482a2da8afa81?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG&f=1","display_name":"JuHyun Lee","link":"https://stackoverflow.com/users/5626619/juhyun-lee"},"is_answered":true,"view_count":659,"accepted_answer_id":34189109,"answer_count":1,"score":2,"last_activity_date":1449695685,"creation_date":1449680798,"question_id":34184756,"link":"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/34184756/using-postman-raw-to-upload-file-to-box-api","title":"Using Postman raw to upload file to box api","body":"<p>I am fairly new to the box api and curl, so forgive me if the question seems little dim.</p>

