"},{"tags":["java","box-api","box","oauth2"],"owner":{"reputation":36,"user_id":5733900,"user_type":"registered","profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/8a7dbc888de94e3233addb6de35132a4?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG&f=1","display_name":"Manas","link":"https://stackoverflow.com/users/5733900/manas"},"is_answered":false,"view_count":393,"answer_count":0,"score":1,"last_activity_date":1468935209,"creation_date":1451564035,"last_edit_date":1468935209,"question_id":34546392,"link":"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/34546392/generating-box-auth-code-for-oauth2-in-programmatic-way","title":"Generating Box Auth code for OAuth2 in programmatic way","body":"<p>I am developing a Java standalone application which uses Java box sdk to access my box account to access files stored there.</p>

<p>I am using <code>OAuth2</code> for authentication to box account. Current steps are:</p>

<ol>
