<strong><a href="https://api.box.com/oauth2/authorize?response_type=code&amp;client_id=[client" rel="nofollow">https://api.box.com/oauth2/authorize?response_type=code&amp;client_id=[client</a> id]&amp;state=authenticated</strong>
in the browser to authorise access to my box account. This is a manual steps where I have intervene to give authorisation to my account.</p></li>
