<p>Although step 2,3,4 is one time activity for a box account but I have to intervene manually to generate auth_code and then execute the application within 30 sec to get refresh token. It become really troublesome if I want to change the box account frequently.</p>

<p>Is there a flexible and programmatic way to handle this.I do not want to intervene manually, so if I want to access another box account it is sufficient for me to change <code>boxId</code> and <code>boxSecret</code> in the application and configure redirect uri for box account and application should be able to take care of steps 2,3 and 4.
