"},{"tags":["box-api"],"owner":{"reputation":9,"user_id":2193685,"user_type":"registered","profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/e618e9eb88d9755a36689963484325b9?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","display_name":"NeedHelpA","link":"https://stackoverflow.com/users/2193685/needhelpa"},"is_answered":false,"view_count":395,"answer_count":0,"score":1,"last_activity_date":1363952840,"creation_date":1363843051,"last_edit_date":1363952840,"question_id":15540063,"link":"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/15540063/cannot-get-access-token-of-box-api-invalid-grant-type-parameter-or-parameter","title":"Cannot get access token of box api &gt; &quot;Invalid grant_type parameter or parameter missing&quot;","body":"<p>No matter whether I use:</p>

<pre><code>https://www.box.com/api/oauth2/token?grant_type=authorization_code&amp;code=OS9wgZP1NkP9e7R7cLbpfnTlMJLCwyIn&amp;client_id=*******&amp;client_secret=*********
