"},{"tags":["java","box-api"],"owner":{"reputation":1,"user_id":2556197,"user_type":"registered","profile_image":"https://i.stack.imgur.com/sQEE0.gif?s=128&g=1","display_name":"sarath thota","link":"https://stackoverflow.com/users/2556197/sarath-thota"},"is_answered":true,"view_count":730,"answer_count":4,"score":0,"last_activity_date":1386887897,"creation_date":1373281298,"last_edit_date":1386853262,"question_id":17525007,"link":"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/17525007/sending-request-to-api-v2-using-access-token-from-box-com-in-java-with-authoriza","title":"Sending Request to API V2 using access_token from box.com in java with Authorization Header","body":"<p>I am trying to develop one web application using JAVA to retrieve files and folders from box.com.</p>

