"},{"tags":["box-api"],"owner":{"reputation":1,"user_id":1289610,"user_type":"registered","profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/f39af2687fafee0951c49a2ab6d4a3d8?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","display_name":"burymm","link":"https://stackoverflow.com/users/1289610/burymm"},"is_answered":false,"view_count":624,"answer_count":1,"score":0,"last_activity_date":1366428814,"creation_date":1366402607,"question_id":16112833,"link":"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/16112833/message-invalid-value-xxx-entity-body-should-be-a-correctly-nested-resource","title":"message: &quot;Invalid value &#39;xxx&#39;. Entity body should be a correctly nested resource attribute name/value pair&quot;","body":"<p>When I try recieve list of folders I get message: "Invalid value 'Authorization=Bearer xxx'. Entity body should be a correctly nested resource attribute name/value pair".</p>

