"},{"tags":[".net","sdk","box-api"],"owner":{"reputation":113,"user_id":556138,"user_type":"registered","profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/b6779abc6db8b0a9862c615a9b8b1cc1?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","display_name":"austriacus","link":"https://stackoverflow.com/users/556138/austriacus"},"is_answered":false,"view_count":84,"answer_count":1,"score":0,"last_activity_date":1389641268,"creation_date":1386076846,"question_id":20352352,"link":"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/20352352/how-to-generate-upload-email-via-boxapi-v2-net-sdk","title":"How to generate upload email via BoxApi V2 .NET SDK","body":"<p>I can't seem to find the equivalent in the BoxAPI.V2 .NET SDK to the following call:</p>

