</code></pre>

<p>So i've searched the web and i found out that i had to set ssl_mod on my server. But when i wrote the LoadModule line in the files and restarted the server it said that the module was already built-in, so i had a look at the configuration. Httpd.conf has those lines:</p>

<pre><code> &lt;IfModule ssl_module&gt;
