"},{"tags":["c#-4.0","box-api"],"owner":{"reputation":36,"user_id":3215480,"user_type":"registered","profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/abbe44a7fb030f4093c4a80463ff9e9c?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG&f=1","display_name":"user3215480","link":"https://stackoverflow.com/users/3215480/user3215480"},"is_answered":false,"view_count":110,"answer_count":1,"score":0,"last_activity_date":1417550567,"creation_date":1417074234,"question_id":27165511,"link":"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/27165511/getting-compile-time-errors-after-installing-box-v2-nuget-package","title":"Getting compile time errors after installing Box.V2 NuGet package","body":"<p>I have installed lates Box.V2 v1.1.4 NuGet package into my C# Class library project that has framework 4.0. After installing project I wrote below piece of code:</p>

